export function getCountryName(language: string, country: Country) {
  if (language === "fr") {
    return frenchCountryNames[country.code];
  }
  return country.name;
}

export function sanitizeCountryName(countryName: string): string {
  return countryName
    .normalize("NFD")
    .replace(/[\u0300-\u036f]/g, "")
    .replace(/[- '()]/g, "")
    .toLowerCase();
}
